User flow			
			
Anywhere (Vis only)	goto Login		
			
Anywhere (User only)	goto Main Page		
			
Anywhere (Vis/User)	goto About		
	goto FAQ		
			
Anywhere Comment	goto Author/Song Info PopUp		
	if own content: do flag comment		
			
Login Page	do Login		
	do Forgot Password		
	goto Register Page		
			
Register Page	do Register		
			
Main Page	goto Upload Page		
	goto Download Page		
	goto Profile PopUp		
	goto Create PL Page		
	goto Change Playlist		
	goto Delete Content Page		
	goto Song PopUP		
	goto (other) User PopUp		
	do delete recent activity entry		
	do search		
			
About Page			
			
FAQ Page			
			
Upload Page	goto enter optional Info Page		Question: Do we auto-direct to next page after something was dropped into field/selected by harddrive or use another UPLOAD button for that?
	do dragdrop content		
	do direct select on harddrive content		
			
Optional Info Page (Song)	do enter info		Note: this can also be the place where we ask the user whether the song is the same as the one we found in case we already have it
	do upload pic		
	goto upload page (with a notification that songs have been uploaded)		
			
Download Page	do select/deselect		
	do download		
			
Create Playlist Page	do select/deselect		
	do create		
			
Delete Content Page	do select/deselect		
	do delete		
			
Change Playlist Page	do select/deselect		
	do comit change		
			
Profile Pop Up	goto Edit Profile PopUp		
	goto other user popUP		
	do flag comment		
	do comment		
			
Other User Pop Up	do comment		
	do add/remove blacklist (i.e. user can't follow you/can't comment on your songs/profile)		
	do follow		
	do accept follow request (similar to below, but used when follow setting is ASK instead of ALL)		
	do reject follower (i.e. stop person from following you without blacklisting them)		
			
Song Pop Up	if own: goto Edit song info PopUP		Note: when clicking on Playlist, instead of PopUp go to the Change Playlist Page
	if own: do flag comment		
	do comment		
			
Edit Profile PopUp	goto Profile PopUp (i.e. leave edit mode without closing the pop up)		
	do change Pic		
	do change required info		
	do change optional info		
	do commit required info changes		
	do commit optional info changes		
	do set NO/ALL/ASK Follow		Note: NO: other users cannot follow you (btn will be greyed out) ALL: all users can follow you withou explicit permission (can still go to individual user info pages to manually reject them) ASK: you need to permit each follow request before they are your follower(
			
Edit Song Info PopUp	goto Song PopUp (i.e. leave edit mode without closing the pop up)		
	do change Pic		
	do change optional info		
	do commit optional info changes		
	do delete (i.e. goto Delete Content Page with this particular Song already ticked)		
			
do Login	goto Main Page		
